title: Rangers leaning on Hamels again in ALDS Game 5 at Toronto
text:
> Texas Rangers leaning on Hamels again in ALDS Game 5 at Toronto Texas Rangers pitcher Cole Hamels throws against the Toronto Blue Jays in the first inning in Game 2 of baseballs American League Division Series in Toronto on Friday, Oct. 9, 2015.
